ygData.messageBody:
Wow I really like the new UI! Well worth the wait! I was out at EQ
Stractics.com and they listed a site that has skins available for the
new UI, I'm going to try out the Mage one tonight! The URL is
http://www.eqinterface.com

I played a little last night, hardly anyone on, kinda nice, the lag
was practically nill! One thing I've noticed was the increased amount
of Orc Centurions, I kept getting jumped on my way from Felwith to
the High Elf city and they spawned quickly! I wonder if this has to
do with the rumored alliance between the Gnolls and Orcs. Hmmmm. I'm
going to try and get my ranger, Durgaa out tonight and see what I can
find.
